Text:
Skyward
Release Date: January 1, 1985. Runtime: 24 min.
The film takes the audience on a dizzy journey in the form of an aerial race, across France: over Normandy, Brittany, the river Loire, Dordogne, Burgundy, Provence, etc., and it all begins and ends in Paris... with Andy Henderson, Daisy Bates, Amanda James, Natasha Wightman and Alex Giannini.
